           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      50                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Si confermano ugualmente le impostazioni (S/N) ? "
