      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga corpo variata                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rewrite [rdb]                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   rew-rec-rdb-000      thru rew-rec-rdb-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo suc-   *
      *                          * cessiva                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

