           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   rf-rdb-dat-reg         .
           move      w-cat-rig-prg        to   rf-rdb-num-prg         .
           move      w-rig-cod-pdc (1)    to   rf-rdb-cod-pdc         .
           move      w-rig-com-rig (1)    to   rf-rdb-com-rig         .
           move      w-rig-dar-ave (1)    to   rf-rdb-dar-ave         .
